title: Fixer Upper S03E03 Small Town Search for Space PDTV.x264-JIVE
description:
Fixer+Upper - Season 3, Episode 3




A Family Searches a Small Town for the Ultimate Open Space

With two kids under the age of ten, Jaime and Kyle Ferguson are drawn to the good schools and spacious lots in the area of McGregor, Texas. They are looking for a house with four bedrooms, an open kitchen, and lots of trees, and hope that Chip and Joanna can help them find the perfect fit.




Original Air Date: 15-Dec-2015
